results.abstract: USSR releases photo of dog said to enjoy space flights; illus

headline.main: An Old Hand at Space Travel, the Russians Say; RUSSIANS SAY DOG TRAVELS IN SPACE

results.snippet: A Soviet photograph of a dog described as an experienced astronaut, or space traveler, has been received here. According to the Russian caption for the picture, the dog is named Malyshka, which means Little One.
results.lead_paragraph: A Soviet photograph of a dog described as an experienced astronaut, or space traveler, has been received here. According to the Russian caption for the picture, the dog is named Malyshka, which means Little One.
